{"tid":1829671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢新型冠狀病毒可能「已感染上千人」","createTime":"2020-01-19T03:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T04:26:18.000Z","uid":321002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef50b86ffdc7a15bcc676206335da44b9844d74","tid":1829671,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51159808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-51159808&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1Gmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=583f2581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51159808</a><br />\n科學家向BBC說，研究顯示，在中國感染這種神秘病毒的人數遠遠超過官方數據。<br />\n<br />\n目前已有41例經中國專家組確診的新型病毒病例，但英國研究者估計，實際數字接近1700例。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月在武漢出現的這種病毒被認為是一種新型冠狀病毒，可能引發肺炎，目前已致2人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n「與一周前相比，我現在更為擔心，」傳染病學家尼爾&middot;弗格森（Neil Ferguson）教授說。<br />\n<br />\n此項研究在倫敦帝國理工學院的MRC全球傳染病分析中心（MRC Centre for Global Infectious Disease Analysis）進行，該中心為包括英國政府和世界衛生組織在內的機構提供諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡和香港一直對來自武漢的乘客進行檢查，美國當局也宣佈從周五（1月17日）開始，在舊金山、洛杉磯和紐約三個主要機場採取類似措施。<br />\n<br />\n到底死左幾多人，冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd62b08834bde31db681d9fab1165ab64abd136","tid":1829671,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"大陛一定無人死,<br />\n有都係其他原因."},{"pid":"c4f70b0c87c78b5b4479648e5fef1bab6108c707","tid":1829671,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dd62b08834bde31db681d9fab1165ab64abd136","tid":1829671,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"大陛一定無人死,<br />\n有都係其他原因."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"同六四一樣<br />\n一個都沒有死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒事兒沒事兒，別給黨添煩添亂"}]}